lead_paragraph: The Sultan has given away his daughter Fatime to Ali Gulib Bey, third son of the Grand Vizler, Reshid Pasha, and han appointed his son-in-law, Mushir, a member of the great council. This is a great Victory of the reform party, of which Reshid Pasha is the real representant.
